{
  "id": "indus_phase11_ctt_full",
  "name": "Indus Phase-11 — CTT-anchored SA, full pipeline",
  "description": "Phase-11 successor to Phase-10 H17.7 graph. Upgrades: full Mahadevan 1977 (M77) corpus (1669 inscriptions / 5361 tokens) instead of CISI-only; expanded suffix/numeral detection in IndusSignRoleClassifier (terminal_relaxed=0.45, M77 + Parpola numeral defaults, repetition heuristic); k-fold cross-validation splitter (k=5) replacing the single 70/30 split; LMGranularityProfiler + GranularityComparison diagnostics on every LM; iconographic anchor priors (Mahadevan/Parpola fish/jar/U readings) wired into Tamil and Luwian SA via IconographicAnchorPin; joint LM + compound-coupling SA acceptance (compound_weight=1.0) using high-PMI bigrams + attested vocab; ShuffledLMNullDistribution per branch for empirical p-value / z-score; KFoldAggregator wrapping the headline recall metric so the report carries mean ± 95% CI placeholders. Vocabularies are 1740 DEDR Dravidian roots (incl. extended kinship/plant/anatomy/verb/noun coverage), 458 Hieroglyphic Luwian lemmas (Hawkins 2000 + Melchert + Yakubovich), and 184 Mycenaean Greek tablet forms (Ventris-Chadwick 1973 + Aura Jorro). Result is written to reports/indus_phase11_ctt_full.json.",
